data.description:
Discover timeless allure in this 3/4 bedroom tudor residence exuding charm and character. Approach the home through a welcoming front porch that sets the stage for the treasures within. Step into the sun-lit living room with hardwood floors, accentuated by coved ceilings that complement the warmth of a fireplace. The spacious and refined dining room invites you in with its leaded glass windows, perfect for cherished gatherings. Delight in the adorable eat-in kitchen, a culinary haven featuring a tile backsplash, ceramic floor, and recessed lighting—a place where style meets functionality. Storage is aplenty
Ascending to the second floor, three generously sized bedrooms await, accompanied by a full bath, Ascend further to discover a large fourth bedroom and  orna versatile bonus room on the third floor—a space brimming with possibilities, ideal for crafting a serene office retreat or an additional leisure area.A full basement with glass block windows, offering potential for further customization to suit your needs. Outside, embrace the convenience of a 2-car garage, an upper deck, and a patio.
Conveniently located mere minutes away from schools, shopping, and dining, this home offers ease of access to the vibrancy of daily life. Moreover, its short commute to downtown Cleveland, hospitals, and University Circle ensures a perfect blend of convenience and metropolitan connectivity.
